item.title: Privacy Policy
item.description: Protecting your privacy is important to us. This privacy policy covers all “Supplies For Moving, Inc.” websites. All of our websites contain similar product line, with slight variations and multiple services. We strive to keep your personal information confidential. By ensuring that you are aware of and understand our Privacy Policy, we can provide you with better service. Please take a moment to read the following policy to learn how we handle your personal information.
